        </section>

        <!-- INTRO SECTION -->
        <section class="content-block">
            <h2>Why GO-CA-TION™ Needs Partners</h2>
            <p>
                GO-CA-TION™ is a calm-travel storytelling project built around three pillars:
                <strong>Travel • Vintage • Handmade</strong>.
                Every episode of Gocation Life explores waterfalls, mills, scenic drives, roadside Americana,
                vintage hunts, and handmade builds — all filmed with intention and heart.
            </p>
            <p>
                To keep the journey moving — and to finish the GO-CA-TION™ van build — we’re inviting partners
                who believe in the mission and want to help power the road ahead.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- VAN STORY -->
        <section class="content-block">
            <h2>The GO-CA-TION™ Van</h2>
            <p>
                The GO-CA-TION™ van isn’t just a vehicle — it’s the mobile studio, workshop, and home base
                behind the entire project. It allows us to reach remote waterfalls, film historic mills and
                covered bridges, explore vintage shops and roadside oddities, and bring calm travel stories
                to viewers who need a quiet escape.
            </p>
            <p>
                Your partnership helps us finish the van build, cover fuel and travel costs, upgrade gear,
                and keep the journey rolling.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- PARTNER BENEFITS -->
        <section class="content-block">
            <h2>What Partners Receive</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>In-Video Recognition:</strong> Your name, brand, or logo featured in GO-CA-TION™ episodes.</li>
                <li><strong>Website + Description Placement:</strong> Links on go-ca-tion.com and YouTube descriptions.</li>
                <li><strong>Brand Shoutouts:</strong> Across Gocation Life, Along the Whimsy Way, and JX of All Trades.</li>
                <li><strong>Behind-the-Scenes Access:</strong> Van build updates, travel plans, and gear upgrades.</li>
                <li><strong>Sponsor Spotlight:</strong> Featured on this GO-CA-TION™ Life Partner page.</li>
                <li><strong>"Powered By" Credits:</strong> Top-tier partners receive dedicated segments in select episodes.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- TIERS -->
        <section class="content-block">
            <h2>Partnership Levels</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Bronze Partner — $50</h3>
                    <p>Your name listed on the GO-CA-TION™ Life Partner page.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Silver Partner — $150</h3>
                    <p>Name + link + shoutout in a Gocation Life episode.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Gold Partner — $500</h3>
                    <p>Logo placement + link + shoutout + sponsor spotlight.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Platinum Partner — $1,000+</h3>
                    <p>"Powered By" credit in episodes + logo placement + spotlight + custom segment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Legacy Partner — $5,000+</h3>
                    <p>Full-van sponsor — your brand becomes part of the GO-CA-TION™ van itself.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <section class="content-block">
            <h2>Ready to Partner?</h2>
